name: Epitome of Beauty
description: This is the Epitome of beauty art piece I created from a deep part of my soul using the gift that god gave me and the music rap portion is done by me. Im the rapper/battle rapper Cannon Jones from Newark and Eo New Jersey and the woman singing goes by Baby M0ms on ig the beat is produced by J Patterns more collections of this on item on the way. Every time you buy 2 or more I use small portions of the profits to help out a small or growing business, a family in need, homeless shelter, the start of a business, and projects to help the community in hopes to be the light of the world to slowly make someones day or life change for the better. Buy 25 and you will get a digital wall piece for free. Whats beautiful to me is making the world a better place and making something out of nothing. follow me on twitter @cannonjones973 and instagram @cannonjones_973
